title: Ebro In The Morning - Rest In Peace Virgil + Ebro’s CYPY to Himself
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 11/29.

Ebro and the crew are back after the Holiday break, they discuss the passing of beloved designer Virgil Abloh (10), Ebro played himself (14) and much more!
